Linde Gas 24/7 Nordics app is for buying gas cylinders and return the empty ones from Linde Gas 24/7 Nordics self-service gaspoint without a help from the Linde agent. As Linde Gas 24/7 Nordics is open 24/7, you can visit the self-service gaspoint anytime by only using the app and not depending on the open hours of Linde agent. The app is easy to use – you need to register to be able to log in to the app. Free of charge. Registered users can use this app to buy, exchange and rent gas cylinders in any of the Linde Gas 24/7 containers. So in order to be able to access this service you have to be a registered user.

For more information please visit one of the following pages:

Swedish users: http://www.linde-gas.se/24_7
Norwegian users: http://www.linde-gas.no/24_7
Estonian users: http://www.linde-gas.ee/24_7
